"""
        Test that the equality operator returns False when comparing two
        GetRequestPayload structs with different key compression types.
        """
a = payloads.GetRequestPayload(key_compression_type=enums.
    KeyCompressionType.EC_PUBLIC_KEY_TYPE_UNCOMPRESSED)
b = payloads.GetRequestPayload(key_compression_type=enums.
    KeyCompressionType.EC_PUBLIC_KEY_TYPE_X9_62_HYBRID)
self.assertTrue(a != b)
self.assertTrue(b != a)
